query:
UPDATE recipeCategories 
SET categoryType = 'ingredient' 
WHERE name IN (
  'Dairy & Other',
  'Fish & Seafood',
  'Ingredient',
  'Oils & Dressings',
  'Produce',
  'Roe & Eggs',
  'Sauces & Condiments',
  'Specialty Items',
  'Toppings & Garnishes'
);
